Inspect the file with cat /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list â it must be a single unbroken line; delete it with sudo rm /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list and recreate it using the heredoc above.
Official reference: https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/
